              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/25172081/" class="">第1215页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/shijianchangsha/" class=" " title="四廢書房主人">四廢書房主人</a>
                (多說好話少吐槽，學好英語趕緊跑)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="25172081">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <div class="ll">
                    <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/25172081/"><img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/view/page_note/small/public/p25172081-17.jpg"></a>
                  </div>
                  <span class="">  

既然有唐代碑刻为证，没有“不”字文意也說得通，那还是不要“不”字为好吧。</span>
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/25172081/">(<span class="">4回应</span>)</a>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-03-15 21:50</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <div class="middle"><img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p25172081-17.jpg" alt=""><br><span class="pic-title"></span></div><div class="middle"><img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p25172081-18.jpg" alt=""><br><span class="pic-title"></span></div><div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>既然有唐代碑刻为证，没有“不”字文意也說得通，那还是不要“不”字为好吧。
